body:
This fix makes the following code fail with a proper warning (`Assigning to input/const variable`):
```systemverilog
module subm(input [1:0] i);
endmodule

module top;
  subm s1(1);
  initial begin
      s1.i = 2; // <- error here
      force s1.i = '1;
  end
endmodule
```

A test `t_force_input_assign_bad` was added to ensure this behavior.
